{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"725677e0-41d5-4610-ad85-f0471f076781","content":"Done. Key points:\n\n- **No API key needed** — the `id-token: write` permission + the `nuget` environment enable OIDC. NuGet.org verifies the token against your trusted publisher config.\n- **`dotnet nuget push` without `--api-key`** — when trusted publishing is configured, NuGet accepts the OIDC token automatically.\n- **Trigger:** pushing a tag like `v1.0.0` kicks off the publish.\n\n**To publish a release:**\n```bash\ngit tag v1.0.0\ngit push origin v1.0.0\n```\n\nMake sure the package ID in your `.csproj` (`<PackageId>`) matches what you registered on nuget.org for the trusted publisher.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c9a9931f-61da-4464-9d00-0be5a60fa896","outputTokens":179,"requestId":"B808:21A16:D2B600:F1490F:69F2A8C1"},"id":"aeea1650-38ff-43e6-be7f-140e3e83e66f","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:56:38.563Z","parentId":"aaf7f2d3-e04b-474a-83e9-2724600d56af"}
